      "content": "it wasnt just a \"reset\" though. i could feel the feedback loop from the nodes. it's like the internet is this giant organism and it was getting too bloated, too predictable. by forcing those specific packet drops, i basically forced a systemic purge. it's better this way, even if people complain about the downtime. they dont realize how much more stable it actually becomes once the rot is cleared out. i basically acted as the immune response.",
